Token.Abstract: This protocol provides delegate methods to receive the updated registration status and the change of the connected product.
Callback delegate method after the application attempts to register.

Parameter.Name: error
Parameter.Abstract: nil if registration is successful. Otherwise it contains NSError object with error codes from DJISDKRegistrationError.

Token.Abstract: Called when the product property changed.

Parameter.Name: oldProduct
Parameter.Abstract: Old product object. Nil if starting up.

Parameter.Name: newProduct
Parameter.Abstract: New product object. Nil if the USB link or WiFi link between the product and phone is disconnected.
